There is one thing I want you to know about my resume and the portfolio site which I face while applying.
My skill and expertise is quite diverse. But not technically literate people do hiring using ATS.
So, everytime I need to apply for a job (on any portal), I need to create/update one of the various versions of my resume, update my portfolio site, rebuild it, and reupload on firebase.

That is why, I maintain the resume in markdown, and have the site has dynamic section like below:

